---
title: Creamy Prawn & Baby Broccoli Curry with Instant Rice & Onion Chutney
description: A seafood curry already sounds indulgent, what if we told you it’s also easy to make. The Mumbai curry sauce adds so much flavour to the prawns and toasted almonds add a nutty crunch that’s always welcomed. To bring in a special element to tonight’s deluxe curry, we’ve added both onion chutney and yoghurt.
